{"tid":1564498,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"32歲巴塞球員非法持槍+故意傷人！被判入獄2年8個月","createTime":"2019-09-12T20:00:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T23:17:53.000Z","uid":173952,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5e81e27269513c5d3922e39c61741fc33eb612b3","tid":1564498,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T20:00:28.000Z","msg":"香港時間9月12日消息，據媒體報導，被巴塞租借到土耳其伊斯坦堡的杜蘭（A.Turan）被判入獄2年8個月。<br />\n  去年10月，杜蘭在酒吧和土耳其歌手Berkay Sahin發生衝突，原因是杜蘭搭訕這位歌手的老婆。衝突導致Berkay Sahin鼻部骨折，隨後杜蘭向地面開槍引起恐慌，他因為非法持槍和故意傷人被判入獄32個月。<br />\n  根據報導，除非杜蘭在未來5年再次犯罪，否則他不會入獄。<br />\n  32歲的杜蘭被巴塞租借在土超球隊伊斯坦堡效力，他曾經代表巴塞出場55次攻入15球，獲得1個西甲冠軍、2個西班牙盃冠軍和1個西班牙超級盃，2018年冬季轉會窗，他被巴塞租借給伊斯坦堡，時間是兩個半賽季。"},{"pid":"67310740fedff75b2b921559ce68c61ea86445cf","tid":1564498,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T20:00:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"749911149233a463ef9b614480ec49a8388e5e70","tid":1564498,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T20:19:13.000Z","msg":"[文長][中期檢討]希望大家入黎睇下我地現有既問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1563440/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1563440/page/1</a><br />\n推左幾粒鐘, 正皮升得好慢, 希望大家可以幫我share出去, 我好有信心呢篇文係可以幫助打破現況<img sr